summary: This is Set Sail, a Skyrim mod like no other.
descriptionHtml:
-----------DESCRIPTION----------- 

There have been rumors of a new privateer business showing up in Dawnstar. Sure enough, right by the docks, there's the building. 
Set Sail puts you in a completely new unexplored Skyrim world. The ocean. Your ship has a full crew ready to explore. Are you? 

WORK IN PROGRESS!! 

-----------INFORMATION----------- 

NO DLCs REQUIRED. 

There shouldn't be any bugs in this mod. If you find any, tell me right away. 

-The door is now moved to Dawnstar. You can't miss it. Check the screenshot above if you need help. 

Thank you to everyone who subscribes! 

Version 1.4 fixed the grey face bug. Huge thanks to jpdoctor! 

Version 1.6
